## Pest control in Kashmir — local context

Kashmir's climate — humid summers, stored winter provisions, and older building stock in parts of Srinagar — creates conditions where pests thrive if left unchecked. Kitchens with persistent moisture, basements and storage rooms, and wooden construction in heritage neighbourhoods all need targeted treatment rather than one-size-fits-all spraying.

When you book through Panun Kaergar, you are hiring professionals who follow approved methods and can adapt treatment to your home. Tell us if you have children, pets, elderly members, or sensitive areas — nursery, kitchen, prayer room — when you book so the technician can plan accordingly. You can describe what you have seen — droppings, bite marks, trails of ants, swarming termites — and the assigned partner arrives prepared.

